data.description:
Beautiful well established home in the heart of Glen Rose. Close to schools, dining, and grocery stores. This home boasts a large family room, wood burning stove, and just over an acre of land. The large shop is perfect for your weekend projects or all those Christmas decorations. RV pad in the back is perfect for guests or to store your RV for vacations. The 5 bedrooms gives you room to spread out and have your own space. Easy commute to Stephenville, Cleburne, and Fort Worth. A must see!!

Sellers are aware that the sub-floor in the living and hall needs to be replaced. They are offering $10,000 in seller concessions to cover this. Homeowners believe the acreage to be 1.042. See survey
